comments.body:
I think we now use bracket syntax for the conditional (after a famous Apple bug iirc)
```diff
-    if (!f) LogPrintf("Failed to write %s \n", latch_filename.c_str());
-    else fclose(f);
+    if (f) {
+        fclose(f);
+    } else {
+        LogPrintf("Failed to write %s\n", latch_filename.c_str());
+    }
```

